  "text": "While an entity is incarnate in this third density at this time he may either learn without consciously knowing what he's doing, or he may learn after he is consciously aware that he is learning in the ways of the Law of One. The second way, it is possible for the entity to greatly accelerate his growth. Is not this correct? I am Ra. This is correct.",
